snippet.title: STAGES OF GRIEF
snippet.description:
An abstract art game exploring aesthetic portrayal of emotion, loosely inspired by the five stages of grief model. Made this game as a part of my Masters Thesis :^)
Check it out here: https://siiins.itch.io/stages-of-grief
Thank you so much if you take the time to check it out!
